README.md
     1â†’# go-multierror
     2â†’
     3â†’[![CircleCI](https://img.shields.io/circleci/build/github/hashicorp/go-multierror/master)](https://circleci.com/gh/hashicorp/go-multierror)
     4â†’[![Go Reference](https://pkg.go.dev/badge/github.com/hashicorp/go-multierror.svg)](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hashicorp/go-multierror)
     5â†’![GitHub go.mod Go version](https://img.shields.io/github/go-mod/go-version/hashicorp/go-multierror)
     6â†’
